<br>
All of the people that had made a moral impact on his unlife were there:<br>
<br>
General Stock<br>
Simon<br>
The Harald<br>
<br>
When he awoke this time, the dream was clear to him.<br>
It created a whole new insight into his problem.<br>
<br>
Dr. Demarco sat up in bed, and looked around him.  it was 4:00pm on wednesday.  He got up, and pulled a bottle out of the refrigerator (that he had converted into a &quot;warmer&quot;) and poured himself a glass of &quot;wine&quot;.<br>
<br>
He glanced down at the book left open on his desk:<br>
<br>
-------------------------------------<br>
Journal entry<br>
Tuesday April 8th, 2003<br>
<br>
Keeper, I know you're watching.<br>
-------------------------------------<br>
<br>
The Doctor slammed the book shut and threw it into his safe, chugged his glass of &quot;wine&quot; and walked back into the lab.<br>
<br>
&quot;I must get back to work&quot; He told himself. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=79.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showNextMessage?topicID=79.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=79.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/ez/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.threadControl?topicID=79.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=79.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=79.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="scbnforum58570frm12">Blackjack's Message Board <option value="scbnforum58570frm21">The Barrens<option value="scbnforum58570frm23">Domain Status<option value="scbnforum58570frm20">SchreckNET™ (Nos only)<option value="scbnforum58570frm18">The Santa Carla Tribune<option value="scbnforum58570frm19">Literary<option value="scbnforum58570frm16">Players Forum<option value="scbnforum58570frm17">Storyteller and Narrator Announcements</select></td><t